OL,3,CMan jailed for 'ferocious attack' on
OL,4,Cpartner
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for repeatedly
OL,7,Fstabbing his partner at their home
OL,8,Fnear Barnsley.
OL,10,FAt 8:38pm on Sunday 2 February, Ian
OL,11,FRothery - 70, of High Street in South
OL,12,FHiendley - called 999 and said he had
OL,13,Fkilled his girlfriend before ending
OL,14,Fthe call. He was called back and
OL,15,Finitially said "forget about it"
OL,16,Fbefore again saying he had killed his
OL,17,Fgirlfriend by stabbing her.
