OL,6,FPolice and paramedics found the
OL,7,Fvictim, now aged 67-years-old, at a
OL,8,Fneighbour's house and took her to
OL,9,Fhospital. She had multiple stab wounds
OL,10,Fto her collar, neck and shoulder, and
OL,11,Finjuries to her face and hands.
OL,13,FCCTV revealed that after initially
OL,14,Fbeing assaulted inside the property,
OL,15,Fthe victim escaped to the front garden
OL,16,Fwhere she was further assaulted by
OL,17,FRothery. He could be seen kicking her
OL,18,Fwhile she laid on the floor.
