OL,6,FThe victim continues to suffer with
OL,7,Fongoing health issues following the
OL,8,Fassault, including breathing
OL,9,Fdifficulties after it was revealed
OL,10,Fthat she also sustained a collapsed
OL,11,Flung from the incident.
OL,13,FRothery appeared at Leeds Crown Court
OL,14,Fon Thursday 14 August. He was
OL,15,Fsentenced to six years and eight
OL,16,Fmonths for causing grievous bodily
OL,17,Fharm with intent.
