OL,4,Cpartner
OL,6,FPC Becky Thompson, who was the officer
OL,7,Fin the case, said: "The complainant
OL,8,Fwas subjected to a ferocious attack
OL,9,Fwhich caused serious injuries and has
OL,10,Fhad a lasting impact.
OL,12,F"Throughout the investigation, she has
OL,13,Fshown immense courage and bravery in
OL,14,Fsupporting a prosecution and assisting
OL,15,Fthe police and CPS to bring the
OL,16,Fdefendant to justice.
OL,18,F"I hope the sentencing brings the
OL,19,Fcomplainant a sense of closure and,
OL,20,Fwith the assistance of family, she can
OL,21,Flook to the future positively.
