OL,6,F"Domestic abuse is not to be
OL,7,Ftolerated, and we encourage any victim
OL,8,Fto report it knowing they will be
OL,9,Flistened to and supported."
OL,11,FThe victim provided victim personal
OL,12,Fstatements to the court.
OL,14,FShe said: "Prior to the incident, I
OL,15,Fwas a fit and healthy woman with no
OL,16,Ffears and only contentment. I had a
OL,17,Flot of pleasures in life, such as dog
OL,18,Fwalking, meeting friends, enjoying my
OL,19,Fvillage walks.
