OL,6,F"The difference to what my life once
OL,7,Fwas to what it has become is
OL,8,Funfathomable. That's because of Ian.
OL,10,F"I've been left hurt, frightened,
OL,11,Fliving with constant pain and flash
OL,12,Fbacks. This is no life. But I know
OL,13,Fwith the help of my family, especially
OL,14,Fmy son and daughter, that I will be
OL,15,Fable to rebuild myself and eventually
OL,16,Fheal.
